        <notes>
          <body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Mass of a 20 um diameter cell (PMID: 15723561)
Logic function updated: if less than the minTumorMass, then tumor mass is zero

Old: 
Tumor_LN1_Mass = ((Tumor_LN1_Mass.Proliferating+Tumor_LN1_Mass.SublethalDamage+Tumor_LN1_Mass.LethalDamage)&gt;minTumorMass)*(Tumor_LN1_Mass.Proliferating+Tumor_LN1_Mass.SublethalDamage+Tumor_LN1_Mass.LethalDamage)+((Tumor_LN1_Mass.Proliferating+Tumor_LN1_Mass.SublethalDamage+Tumor_LN1_Mass.LethalDamage)&lt;=minTumorMass)*minTumorMass</body>
        </notes>
      </parameter>
